'''Roger Federer''' d amyurar n waddal n [[Tennis]] tmurt [[Taswist]], ilul ass n 8 ɣuct 1981 di temdint n [[Bâle]].
Yebda yetturar d terbaɛt tameqqṛant aseggas n 1998, yeḥrez amḍiq amenzu n ubellez n ATP azal n 237 imalas yemseḍfaren (285 ḥalarmi d 6 Yunyu 2010). Ass n 8 Yulyu 2012, yewwi tadwilt n Wimbledon i tikkelt tis sebɛa, yeqḍa-d amyurar [[Pete Sampras]] deg umḍan n tedwilin n Wimbledon i yeḥrez akked imalas i yella di tqacucut n ubellez n ATP (Imalas wis 286). ([[Roger Federer|'''Kemmel leqraya'''...]])
